{"tid":42061,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"csl客服熱線好蠱惑","createTime":"2016-12-16T11:09:26.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-16T12:40:57.000Z","uid":9722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"14436a01320eec57a54ea2c4cf24d837db828342","tid":42061,"uid":9722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T11:09:26.000Z","msg":"有無巴打絲打有相同遭遇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 想問翻d嘢 用csl個號碼打去csl 等等等等等勁耐都無人聽 仲要喺打成幾次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 之後我就出於好奇心用其他唔喺csl嘅號碼打啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 一分鐘都無 就已經聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a66fb360155529eca10c90af2e65b00780a1a3a","tid":42061,"uid":35814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T11:11:24.000Z","msg":"唔一定<br />\n時快時慢<br />\n但最煩係啲選擇好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f20181f6c37000b75b8979f386a2a5d1b93ca5e","tid":42061,"uid":9722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T11:25:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔一定<br />\n時快時慢<br />\n但最煩係啲選擇好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我覺得係新客戶優先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 因為我csl號碼打選咩更改帳號資料之類嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 而其他號碼我係選咩手機服務計畫 （csl個號碼無呢個揀）而且仲一早戴定頭盔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/s